ss":"review of souls, last judgment"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"memoir, petition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"offer, proposition, motion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"side"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"collection of clouds"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"commodity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"goods, merchandise, movables"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"breadth, width"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"latitude"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"midst, middle","examples":[{"text":"عَرْض الشَّيْء","english":"the thing itself"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mountain"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"base of a mountain"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"army"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"locusts"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عُرِضَ (ʕuriḍa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"compensation, substitute"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"madness, possession by a jinn"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hour"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"symptom, characteristic, accident as opposed to substance, what exposes another thing to view, manifestation","examples":[{"text":"تَخَلَّصَ مِنَ ٱلْأَعْرَاضِ فَقَطْ.","english":"He only got rid of the symptoms."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"accident (appearance, manifestation)","examples":[{"text":"Coordinate term: ذَات (ḏāt, “essence”)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tract, quarter, low land"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"blame, attribution of vice, reproach, reputation","examples":[{"text":"طَرِبَ الشيْخُ فغنّى، واصْطبحْ\nمن عُقارٍ تُنهبُ الهمّ الفَرَحْ\nأخَذتْ من كلّ شيءٍ لَوْنَهــا،\nهي في ناجودها قوْسُ قُزَحْ\nشيْخُ لذّاتٍ، نقِيٌّ عِرْضُهُ،\nتحْسُنُ الأشعارُ فيه، والمِدَحْ.\nلا تراهُ الدّهْرُ إلاّ ثَمِلاً،\nبينَ إبْريقٍ، وزِقٍّ، وقدَحْ","english":"The shaykh gleed and sang and craved more booze\nforthy delight removes the sorrow.\nHe obtained from every thing its hues\nand his cup exposed a rainbow.\nShaykh of bliss, no way blammed,\nThe notes of him are merry, fele to plaud,\nFate sees him not but slammed,\nbetwixe ewer and wineskin, beaker-pawed."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of عَرُضَ (ʕaruḍa) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕa.ra.dˤa/","/ʕa.ru.dˤa/","/ʕu.ri.dˤa/","/ʕar.ra.dˤa/","/ʕardˤ/","/ʕa.radˤ/","/ʕirdˤ/","/ʕi.radˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28694","headword_ar":"عَرْضِىٌّ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaroD`Y","text_ar":"عَرْضٰى"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A kind of cloths"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garments."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Certain of the appertenances"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAfiq","text_ar":"مَرَافِق"},{"kind":"text","text":", O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and chambers"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the house:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a word of the dial. of El-'Irák: (O, K:) unknown to the Arabs. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n28695","headword_ar":"عُرْضِىٌّ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"A camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that goes obliquely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclining towards one side, because not yet completely trained:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"submissive in the middle part"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body, so as to be easy to ride, but"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult of management:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perverse, untoward,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intractable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", a she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not completely trained:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult to manage; refractory."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaruwDN","text_ar":"عَرُوضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who does not sit steadily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"firmly, upon the saddle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inclining at one time this way, and at another time that way."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n28698","headword_ar":"عِرَضَّى","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiriD~aY","text_ar":"عِرِضَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zimik~aY","text_ar":"زِمِكَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Briskness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightliness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraDonapN","text_ar":"عِرَضْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b2-  And [app. for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uw EiraD~aY","text_ar":"ذُو عِرَضَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Brisk, lively,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See, again,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraDonapN","text_ar":"عِرَضْنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28708","headword_ar":"عَرُضِىٌّ","root":"ErD","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relating to, prosody,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the art of versification. A prosodist."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}